<seg id="1049">"the recursive method starts with 4 beams per pixel. if the difference between the color values exceeds the given threshold, then the pixel is divided into 4 sub-pixels, which are individually followed and tested for further subdivision. the maximum depth of recursion allows you to set the depth value."</seg>
